Usage: createTrack [-help] -dir <string> -layer <string> -num <integer>
                   -start <float> -step <float>

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-dir <string>           # track direction (string, required)
-layer <string>         # layer name list (string, required)
-num <integer>          # number of track (int, required)
-start <float>          # start coordinate (float, required)
-step <float>           # step of track (float, required)